Another Siberian, Benazir Zhamalova, 20, also a student in Novosibirsk, won the title Miss Brunette.

Miss Strashevskaya, a student from the Novosibirsk Institute of Law, has vows not to be distracted by modelling offers or sudden fame after her win in an online poll run by Miss Russia.

She said: 'I have wanted to be a lawyer since school and deliberately came to this institute.

'I will not leave it under any circumstances and in the future I want to engage in civil law.

'Part of the money, I plan to spend on a gift for my parents and more I want to donate to children with cancer.

